originalText.text: Booked a spot in this garage over the weekend through spot hero. When I arrived at the garage for my reservation the attendant told me there was no space and I should “just cancel” my reservation. Ended up having to find street parking for the whole weekend. Spot hero was great and refunded me for the weekend, but since I “cancelled” the reservation to get the refund I couldn’t leave a review on spot hero about the place. Was very disappointing and wouldn’t trust this place if booked on spot hero

originalText.text: Reserved a garage on spothero.  Came to this garage and the attendant asked for a bar code, we handed to him, he scanned in and he said great no problem, see you tomorrow. Today we came at the appropriate time to pick up the car, and were told we needed to pay double in addition to what was on the ticket because it was the wrong garage.  Apparently the one reserved was next door.  When we said the ticket was scanned yesterday, they said nothing can be done.  We weren't allowed to speak to a manager or have anyone's name. Absolute scam.  BEWARE.
